    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed at $33,000, a price that honestly reflects its good condition \u2014 and we want to be fully transparent about what that means. The exterior presents well overall: the paint retains a healthy shine with only minor surface blemishes and the occasional small scratch or scuff you'd expect from normal use, but nothing that detracts significantly from its appearance. The body panels are straight and well-aligned, with no signs of major dents or collision damage. The interior is clean and functional \u2014 the seats show modest wear consistent with regular use, the dashboard and trim are intact, and all major controls and features operate as intended. Mechanically, the car runs reliably and has been maintained adequately; you can expect dependable day-to-day performance. This is a solid, honest vehicle for a buyer who wants a good-quality used car without paying mint-condition prices.",
      "price": 33000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 **Budget-Friendly Fixer or Parts Car \u2014 Priced to Reflect Its Condition!** Looking for an affordable vehicle or a project car? This one could be your opportunity! We want to be upfront: this car is in poor condition, showing significant wear and likely in need of notable repairs before it's road-ready at its best. It does still have some life in it, and at this price point, it could be a great fit for a handy buyer, a mechanic, or someone needing basic transportation on a tight budget. No surprises here \u2014 what you see is what you get, honestly priced for its current state!",
      "price": 6500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Honest Value, Real Utility \u2014 A Practical Pick for the Savvy Shopper! This used car is in fair condition, and we want to set the right expectations \u2014 it's a solid, functional vehicle that gets the job done! You'll notice some wear and minor imperfections that come with age and use, but mechanically it's holding its own and ready for daily driving. It's not perfect, but it's priced to reflect exactly what it is \u2014 a dependable, no-nonsense ride for someone who values practicality over polish. If you need reliable transportation without the premium price tag, this one deserves a look!",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly exceptional, mint condition \u2014 an increasingly rare find in the used car market. The exterior finish is flawless, showing absolutely no scratches, dents, swirl marks, or paint fade; it looks as though it just rolled off the showroom floor. The interior is equally immaculate, with spotless upholstery, clean carpets, and all controls, displays, and features functioning perfectly. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, with all fluid levels correct and no leaks, unusual noises, or warning lights. The tires have excellent tread depth remaining, the brakes are responsive and in great shape, and the suspension feels tight and precise. This is a vehicle that has clearly been owned and maintained with exceptional care, and a pre-purchase inspection will confirm everything described here. A buyer looking for a used car that truly rivals a new one in condition will not be disappointed.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project car or a bare-bones runner? This vehicle is priced to reflect its current condition \u2014 it has seen better days and will need some attention and repairs to get it back in shape. There are visible wear and cosmetic issues throughout, and mechanically it will require work. That said, it's an honest deal for the right buyer who's handy or looking for an affordable entry-level option. What you see is what you get \u2014 no surprises!",
      "price": 6500.0,
