      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in fair condition and is priced to reflect its current state honestly. It is a functional, drivable car that gets the job done, but buyers should expect visible signs of age and use throughout. The exterior shows noticeable wear including light scratches, minor dents or dings, and some paint fading \u2014 nothing catastrophic, but clearly a car that has lived its life on the road. The interior is similarly worn, with scuffs on surfaces, some fading on upholstery, and general signs of regular use. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though we recommend a pre-purchase inspection as there may be deferred maintenance or minor repairs needed to bring it fully up to par. This is a solid choice for a budget-conscious buyer who needs reliable transportation and doesn't mind putting a little work or money into the vehicle over time.",
